  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个联邦学习平台设计一个ER图，核心是DataManager和ComputeTask这两个实体。DataManager可以打开多个DataSample，这个关系要体现出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataManager",
        "DataSample",
        "opens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，DataManager对DataSample是一对多。那ComputeTask这边呢？它应该归属于某个ComputePlan吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ComputeTask",
        "ComputePlan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ComputeTask必须属于一个ComputePlan，是多对一的关系。另外每个ComputeTask要执行一个Function，这个也要连上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ComputeTask",
        "ComputePlan",
        "belongs to",
        "Function",
        "execute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把ComputeTask到ComputePlan的belongs to关系，以及到Function的execute关系都画好了。接下来是任务数据的部分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ComputeTask",
        "ComputePlan",
        "Function"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，任务数据有三种：TrainTaskData、TestTaskData，还有AggregateTaskData和CompositeTaskData。它们都是ComputeTask的特化，用specializes关系。TrainTaskData会produce一个Model，同时也要use DataManager和DataSample。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TrainTaskData",
        "ComputeTask",
        "specializes",
        "Model",
        "produces",
        "DataManager",
        "DataSample",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "TrainTaskData画好了。TestTaskData类似吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TrainTaskData"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TestTaskData也是specializes ComputeTask，但它比较特殊——它要evaluates一个Function，然后produce的是Performance而不是Model。DataManager和DataSample的使用关系保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TestTaskData",
        "ComputeTask",
        "specializes",
        "Function",
        "evaluates",
        "Performance",
        "produces",
        "DataManager",
        "DataSample",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，TestTaskData产出Performance。那AggregateTaskData和CompositeTaskData呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TestTaskData",
        "Performance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "AggregateTaskData相对简单，specializes ComputeTask并produce一个Model。CompositeTaskData也是specializes ComputeTask并produce Model，但注意它会产生两个Model，所以标注一下\"produces (x2)\"。另外CompositeTaskData也需要use DataManager和DataSample。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AggregateTaskData",
        "CompositeTaskData",
        "ComputeTask",
        "specializes",
        "Model",
        "produces",
        "DataManager",
        "DataSample",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "都加上了。最后Model实体需要加属性吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AggregateTaskData",
        "CompositeTaskData",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Model要加一个category属性，类型是ModelCategory。这样整个结构就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Model",
        "ModelCategory",
        "category"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Model的category属性已添加。我整体检查一下：DataManager管理DataSample，ComputeTask归属ComputePlan并执行Function，四种任务数据分别特化ComputeTask，Train和Aggregate和Composite产生Model（Composite是x2），Test产生Performance，Model带category属性。是这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataManager",
        "DataSample",
        "ComputeTask",
        "ComputePlan",
        "Function",
        "TrainTaskData",
        "TestTaskData",
        "AggregateTaskData",
